					<p>This is a cool way to write your way out of a writer&#8217;s block. Nice mix of themes and the obsession over an idiom has a very familiar feel &#8211; the way something you say all the time suddenly jumps into focus and you realise what you&#8217;ve been saying and ask what the hell does it mean?</p>
