					<p>This is one of my favourites.<br />
I really liked the discussion of writer&#8217;s block and felt much the same when trying to write for my own theme some weeks ago. A difficult interesting think to talk about and the revolutions around the idiom are cute.</p>
<p>In the second sentence I assume you meant &#8216;phrase&#8217; not &#8216;phase&#8217; and this caused me some confusion.</p>
<p>&#8216;Take a firm grip&#8230;&#8217; &#8211; great sentence.</p>
<p>I was less keen on the italics paragraph but it worked okay for me. The last line seems a little out of context &#8211; somehow the breaking down between writing micfic and talking about micfic bugged me here.</p>
